{{!--
  OPERATING MODEL V2 — Evidence Carousel

  Three categories (Products, Systems, Teams) with evidence carousels
  Scroll-driven experience: heading transitions at category boundaries
  Particle morphing: sphere → triple-sphere → torus

  Card modes:
  - screenshot: image only
  - video: mp4 video
  - text: custom formatted text
  - metric: reuse stats-parallax card styling
--}}

<section class="operating-model-v2" id="operating-model-v2">
  <div class="om-stage">

    {{!-- PRODUCTS CATEGORY --}}
